{"tid":796206,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【終於閃人】轉投比錫達斯 卡利奧斯感謝利迷：永不獨行","createTime":"2018-08-27T15:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T17:49:58.000Z","uid":147522,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"78141c983d82a5ad6907f9e4629a96361341b09f","tid":796206,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:02:48.000Z","msg":"利物浦門將卡利奧斯落實以借用身份轉投土耳其球隊比錫達斯，臨別時他特意在社交平台感謝球迷支持，指他們讓自己感受到「永遠不會獨行」。<br />\n這位 25 歲德國門將於 Instagram 上載一張手持比錫達斯球衣的相片，他首先表示很驕傲成為比錫達斯的新成員，並會盡力為球隊爭取勝利，與此同時，他又感謝舊東家利物浦球迷的支持，讓他感到永遠不會獨行。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n卡利奧斯於上屆歐聯決賽面對皇家馬德里中，兩度犯上大錯，直接令球隊輸波，根據租用協議，他將會租借至比錫達斯兩年，如果達到指定要求，比錫達斯將要以 725 萬英鎊將他買斷。"},{"pid":"a18ae103b8e0a4ec749110d4de25056b43eafabf","tid":796206,"uid":13718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:59:06.000Z","msg":"我宣布猁狗全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16f2fda5d6184873790fcfdc1f594d726d4ff24","tid":796206,"uid":56649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"永不獨行但又被人賣走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade8c16d119e621523d92bd29dad613dd67e6fc8","tid":796206,"uid":145021,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b16f2fda5d6184873790fcfdc1f594d726d4ff24","tid":796206,"uid":56649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"永不獨行但又被人賣走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"有咩衝突呢<br />\n咁個個球員都唔使走 隊波成立到而家係咪有幾千人？"},{"pid":"495359206b45d57810e220b79896fdb33da75631","tid":796206,"uid":1790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"You never work again<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb16a2